>> source: https://wicworks.fns.usda.gov/recipe/golden-milk
>> serves: 1
>> total time: 10 minutes

Combine the @soy milk{1%cup}, @honey{2%tsp}, @almond butter (optional){1.5%tsp}, @vanilla{1/2%tsp}, @cinnamon{1/2%tsp}, @turmeric{1/4%tsp}, @ginger{1/8%tsp}, and any optional spices in a #small saucepan{}.

Heat over medium until warmed through, whisking briskly so that the almond butter does not stick to the bottom and the spices incorporate. Do not let boil.
